    ScaleFactor: float
        Setting for the window scale factor.
    Size: list[float]
        Setting for the window size.
    Theme: WindowTheme
        Setting for the window theme(background color) using Color
    Title: str
        Setting for the window title.
    Transparent: bool
        Whetehr the window background is transparent.
    '''
